properties.title: Independence Day 2011 Parade
properties.description: dave_mcmt posted a photo: The 2011 Independence Day Parade, Main Street, Miles City, Montana. Frank Stoltz of Miles City, founder of Frank's Body Shop, was the grand marshal of the 2011 parade. Frank drove this 1955 Chevrolet wrecker which he bought new. The wrecker reportedly has only 47,000 original miles on it. (July 4, 2011) Here's a nice article about Frank: www.montanatowing.com/frankstoltz.html Photo courtesy of Mark Wiedeman.
